Installing Express...
npm install express --save
to save library into package.json
when you do npm install  also install this
API rest with nodejs

Installing Bcrypt...
npm install bcrypt-nodejs
library to encrpyt pass

Installing body parser ...
npm install body-parser
to parse thow json and work with objects

Installing connect...
upload files with node protocol http
files can have protocol
npm install connect-multiparty --save

Installing jwt...
npm install jwt-simple --save
authentication with tokens

Installint moment...
npm install moment --save
to use it later

Installing Mongoose....
to work with mongodb
npm install mongoose --save

Installing mongoose pagination...
to make an example of pagination
npm install mongoose-pagination

Installing nodemon...
every time we make a change updload server 
npm install nodemon --save-dev
only to use it in dev
